<div id="Idea_2605"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2605-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2605">Line Item Vote/Veto&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">xaztec</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Congress should have the ability to vote on each line item in a bill rather than the current all-or-nothing approach.  the president should also have line item veto power.  </div>
